latestIgtvVideos.title: Homemade Peanut Butter Recipe.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients:
1 kg peanuts
200 g dark compound 
Honey (if needed)

1kg peanuts: 130 Rs/ kg
200 g dark compound: 45 Rs/ kg
 Max 200 rs for : 1 kg+ peanut butter

Take raw peanuts, roast them till they get brow.. roast evenly and continuously to avoid burns that taste bitter. 

Peel off the skin and put the peanuts in the grinder. Grind it to fine particles add a piece of dark chocolate compound and then grind it again and again till smooth paste.

Macros Breakdown:
Calories: 6810
Protein: 267 g
Carbs: 276 g
Fats: 562 g
